## Prerequisites

- Node.js 20+
- npm

## Installation

```bash
npm install
npx playwright install
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
npm test

# Run tests in headed mode
npm run test:headed


# Run tests in parallel
npm run test:parallel

# View HTML report
npm run report
```

## Environment Configuration

Update test data in:
- `data/dev.json` - Development environment
- `data/qa.json` - QA environment

Set environment with `TEST_ENV=qa npm test`

## Page Objects

All page objects extend `BasePage` and are located in the `pages/` directory:
- `LoginPage.ts` - Login page interactions
- `HomePage.ts` - Home page interactions

## Test Structure

```
tests/
├── login.test.ts # Login functionality tests
├── smoke.test.ts # Smoke tests
└── setup.ts # Test configuration
```

